subtitleNullable: 17 classes in 4 categorys for image classification.
descriptionNullable:
This dataset has been created for the 2021 Jugend Forscht competition. It contains 42500 Images with a size of 500x500.

There are 17 classes. Each class has 2000 train and 500 test images. The classes are divided into four categories: Rubber Toy, Pig Head, Lego, and Chips. The classes are variations of the overall category. These variations can differ in Color, Pattern, and Form.

For example, the images of class 2 and 3 are both part of the category Rubber Toy and the images of class 10 and 11 are both part of the category Lego.
